* Concurrent\nRun Control
** Problem
***_ Run takes longer than interval
***_ Next run starts before previous ends
***_ Risk: data corruption / duplicates
** Max Concurrent Runs
***_ Default: multiple allowed
***_ Set to 1 for non-overlapping jobs
** Queue Behavior
*** Queue the run
****_ Waits for a slot
****_ No triggers missed
*** Cancel the run
****_ Immediately discarded
****_ Stale triggers not valuable
*** Skip the run
****_ Similar to cancel
****_ Occasional misses acceptable
@endmindmap
